            content: "<div><div><h1 id='estate-planning-documents'>Estate Planning Documents</h1></div><div><h2 id='last-will-and-testament'>Last Will and Testament</h2></div><div><h3 id='i.-introduction'>I. Introduction</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Name</strong>: [Your Full Name]</p></li><li><p><strong>Date of Birth</strong>: [Your Date of Birth]</p></li><li><p><strong>Address</strong>: [Your Address]</p></li><li><p><strong>City, State, ZIP</strong>: [City, State, ZIP Code]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='ii.-executor'>II. Executor</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Executor</strong>: [Name of Executor]</p></li><li><p><strong>Alternate Executor</strong>: [Name of Alternate Executor]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='iii.-distribution-of-assets'>III. Distribution of Assets</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Beneficiaries</strong>:</p></li><li><p>[Name of Beneficiary 1]</p></li><li><p>[Name of Beneficiary 2]</p></li><li><p>&hellip;</p></li><li><p><strong>Distribution of Assets</strong>:</p></li><li><p>[Specify assets and their distribution]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='iv.-guardianship-for-minors'>IV. Guardianship for Minors</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Guardian for Minor Children</strong>: [Name of Guardian]</p></li><li><p><strong>Alternate Guardian</strong>: [Name of Alternate Guardian]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='v.-funeral-and-burial-instructions'>V. Funeral and Burial Instructions</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Funeral Wishes</strong>: [Specify your funeral wishes]</p></li><li><p><strong>Burial Instructions</strong>: [Specify your burial or cremation instructions]</p></li></ul></div><div><h2 id='living-will'>Living Will</h2></div><div><h3 id='i.-healthcare-agent'>I. Healthcare Agent</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Healthcare Agent</strong>: [Name of Healthcare Agent]</p></li><li><p><strong>Alternate Healthcare Agent</strong>: [Name of Alternate Healthcare Agent]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='ii.-medical-treatment-preferences'>II. Medical Treatment Preferences</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>End-of-Life Care</strong>: [Specify your preferences for end-of-life care]</p></li><li><p><strong>Organ Donation</strong>: [Specify your organ donation preferences]</p></li></ul></div><div><h2 id='financial-power-of-attorney'>Financial Power of Attorney</h2></div><div><h3 id='i.-agent'>I. Agent</h3></div><div><ul><li><p><strong>Financial Agent</strong>: [Name of Financial Agent]</p></li><li><p><strong>Alternate Financial Agent</strong>: [Name of Alternate Financial Agent]</p></li></ul></div><div><h3 id='ii.-powers-granted'>II. Powers Granted</h3></div><div><ul><li><strong>Authority</strong>: [Specify the financial powers granted to the agent]</li></ul></div><div><h2 id='additional-instructions'>Additional Instructions</h2></div><div><ul><li>[Include any additional instructions or wishes you may have]</li></ul></div><div><hr></div><div><p><strong>Note</strong>: This is a sample template for estate planning documents. It is essential to consult with a qualified attorney to create legally binding and personalized estate planning documents tailored to your specific needs and jurisdictional requirements.</p></div></div><div></div>",
